text: Wilberfoss is a village and civil parish in the East Riding of Yorkshire, England. It is on the north side of the A1079 about east of York city centre. It is northwest of Market Weighton. According to the 2011 census, 1,866 people live in Wilberfoss parish. That is 11 more than were living there ten years earlier. ==References== Category:Villages in England Category:Civil parishes in England Category:Settlements in the East Riding of Yorkshire
